<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UltraBot — The all-in-one Discord bot</title>
    <meta name="description" content="UltraBot is the modern, all-in-one Discord bot for moderation, music, AI, leveling, economy and more.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="mesh-bg"><div class="grid"></div><div class="blob-3"></div></div>

    <header class="topbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
            <span class="brand-mark"></span>
            <span>UltraBot</span>
        </a>
        <div class="topbar-right">
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Open Dashboard →</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login with Discord</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Online &amp; ready · Updated for 2026</div>
            <h1>Run a smarter server with <span class="grad">UltraBot</span></h1>
            <p class="lead">A modern, self-hosted Discord bot built for serious communities. Moderation, music, AI chat, leveling, economy, and live news — configured from a beautiful dashboard.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                <% } %>
                <a href="https://github.com/theshield2594/ultrabot" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Source</a>
            </div>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">8+</div><div class="stat-label">Modules</div></div>
                <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">24/7</div><div class="stat-label">Uptime</div></div>
                <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">2</div><div class="stat-label">AI Providers</div></div>
                <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">∞</div><div class="stat-label">Servers</div></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Everything your community needs</h2>
                <p>One bot. Every essential module. Configured in clicks, not config files.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
                    <h3>Smart Moderation</h3>
                    <p>Auto-mod, spam &amp; invite filters, link controls, and a full audit log channel.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">🎵</div>
                    <h3>High-Fidelity Music</h3>
                    <p>Smooth 24/7 streaming with queue management, DJ roles, and per-server volume.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">🧠</div>
                    <h3>AI Chat</h3>
                    <p>Bring your own key — OpenAI or Google Gemini — with custom system prompts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">📈</div>
                    <h3>Leveling &amp; XP</h3>
                    <p>Reward active members with tunable XP rates and customizable level-up messages.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">💎</div>
                    <h3>Economy</h3>
                    <p>Daily rewards, work payouts, currency symbols — tweak everything from the dashboard.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">📰</div>
                    <h3>RSS &amp; Daily Digest</h3>
                    <p>Pipe any feed into a channel or aggregate them into a clean daily news digest.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">👋</div>
                    <h3>Welcome Cards</h3>
                    <p>Greet new members with rich, branded welcome messages and image cards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="icon">⚙️</div>
                    <h3>Self-Hosted</h3>
                    <p>You own the data. Drop it on Docker, Portainer, or bare metal in minutes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section" style="padding-top:2rem;">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Ready to power up your server?</h2>
                <p>Sign in with Discord and configure UltraBot in under two minutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Open Dashboard</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login with Discord</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UltraBot · Built for modern Discord communities
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Subtle pointer-tracked glow on feature cards
        document.querySelectorAll('.feature').forEach(card => {
            card.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
                const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
                card.style.setProperty('--mx', `${e.clientX - rect.left}px`);
                card.style.setProperty('--my', `${e.clientY - rect.top}px`);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
